Step 1: Database Setup (XAMPP)
Open XAMPP Control Panel and start Apache and MySQL.
Go to http://localhost/phpmyadmin/.
Create a database named todo_db.
Run this SQL in the SQL tab to create the table:

CREATE TABLE todos (
  id VARCHAR(36) PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  status ENUM('Coming Up', 'Due', 'Overdue', 'Done') DEFAULT 'Coming Up',
  createdAt DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updatedAt DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

Test the api in a postman
### Create a Todo
POST http://localhost:3000/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy Milk",
  "description": "Need it for coffee"
}

### Get all Todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos

### Get one of the Todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/id

### Update a Todo (Mark as Done)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/todos/id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Done"
}

### Delete a Todo 
DELETE http://localhost:3000/todos/id
